based on Alex MacCaw (author of Juggernaut and Spine) demo spine.rails3

=== installation

gem 'juggernaut'
include juggernaut_assets_tags in layout
require juggernaut_handler in application.js


Add an initializer juggernaut.rb with 

SpineJuggernautRails.config.register = :page

=== session_id

Add to the model
attr_accessor :session_id 

add session_id to controller (protected method)
	@page.session_id = session_id (create, update, destroy)

TODO: make a module

=== observers

create an observer for the model and include SpineJuggernautRails::Observer
config/application.rb => 
	config.active_record.observers = :model_observer 


